</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="126" pageNumber="404" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="126.[173,1379,2072,2697]" pageId="126" pageNumber="404">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[175,309,2466,2499]" pageId="126" pageNumber="404">Breeding.</emphasis>
An adult female Voss’s Fish-eating Rat was captured with two large embryos in mid-May, and another was lactating in August.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[174,946,2550,2579]" pageId="126" pageNumber="404" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="126.[173,1379,2072,2697]" box="[174,946,2550,2579]" pageId="126" pageNumber="404">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[174,409,2550,2579]" pageId="126" pageNumber="404">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Voss’s Fish-eating Rats is semi-aquatic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
